## Next Steps for Project Team

To enable Speed Insights data collection on Vercel:

1. **Enable in Vercel Dashboard**
   - Navigate to your Vercel project dashboard
   - Select "Speed Insights" from the sidebar
   - Click "Enable" button
   - This will activate the Speed Insights routes after next deployment

2. **Deploy to Vercel**
   - Deploy the application to Vercel (via Git integration or CLI)
   - The tracking script will automatically be injected

3. **Monitor Performance**
   - After deployment, wait for users to visit your site
   - Performance metrics will appear in the dashboard within a few days
   - View Core Web Vitals and other performance indicators

## Documentation Reference
Installation followed the official Vercel Speed Insights quickstart guide:
https://vercel.com/docs/speed-insights/quickstart

The implementation matches the recommended setup for Next.js App Router (v13.5+).
